snippet.title: Shadow of the Tomb Raider - The Grand Caiman [ESRB]
snippet.description:
Survive the wrath of a Maya god before his vengeance rains destruction across the world available in the Season Pass: https://TombRaider.Games/GrandCaiman12

To protect villagers from the aggression of Trinity, Lara Croft must hunt mercenaries, face the towering wrath of a volcanic new challenge tomb, and survive the lethal surprise concealed within. Equip the Force of Chaos Gear pack and charge into the fray with the Reptile Hide outfit and Whispering Scourge shotgun.

Subscribe to our channel to keep up-to-date with all things Tomb Raider and Lara Croft: https://www.youtube.com/user/tombraider?sub_confirmation=1
